➜比尔·盖茨做蛋糕为巴菲特90岁庆生：他像一年级学生一样吃饭
http://www.sohu.com/a/415770286_116237	30850
<div id="sohuplayer">
<script type="text/javascript" src="//tv.sohu.com/upload/swf/showVrsPlayer.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript">
